<p>Delmarva Power participates in Delaware's net metering program, crediting solar customers at retail electricity rates for excess generation. The utility also offers rebates for high-efficiency HVAC equipment, with incentives ranging from \$300 to \$1,200 for ENERGY STAR certified systems. Additionally, Newark residents may qualify for low-interest solar loans through Delaware's Clean Energy Loan Program, offering financing at rates significantly below typical home improvement loans. Property tax exemptions for solar installations ensure that increased home values from solar systems don't result in higher property taxes.</p>

